How Star Wars Changed the World
A warm, celebratory look at the ways in which the Star Wars universe has inspired countless individuals. The passions, loves and good humour of fans are demonstrated through activities such as building and designing droids, adhering to the scriptures of Jediism, perfecting skills in lightsaber duels, designing and maintaining a highly expensive Wookie costume and making a replica cockpit of the Millennium Falcon.
